rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, thanks for coming!
As you can see, we made it to
Superbia safely.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0002
rows.name:
I feel bad about what I did to
Riana's parents, but...

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0003
rows.name:
Her happiness is what's most
important, after all.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, right, I prepared a thank-you gift for you.
Please take it.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0101
rows.name:
Life in Superbia might be
hard on Riana.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0102
rows.name:
The trouble with Invidia, the fact that
the Divine Beast is weakening... there's no end
to the worries.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0103
rows.name:
But I've sworn to support Riana with all my might
and make her happy! Just you watch!
